Class CmpFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • FileType
      • CmpFile

  • public class CmpFile
extends FileType
    Author:
    Tian Low ttl2132 This class creates or gets an existing .cmp file and manipulates its content, including inserting, deleting, or changing lines, as well as printing its contents. This class executes the methods called by KeyChoice for a .cmp file.
